This paper is primarily focused on reinforcement learning and inverse reinforcement learning, which are subfields of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories. The paper also deals with modeling human behavior and preferences, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper uses simulations and real-world tasks, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV) or robotics (cs.RO).
